OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny morning fog patches quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a fine and sunny day
OL,7,Ffor all. Winds light, so feeling very
OL,8,Fwarm or hot in the strong July
OL,9,Fsunshine. Staying cooler towards the
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPlenty of sunshine through
OL,13,Fthe evening, then staying clear
OL,14,Fovernight. Some mist and fog patches
OL,15,Fforming during the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
