OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FMorning mist and fog patches
OL,6,Fquickly clearing to leave a fine and
OL,7,Fvery warm, locally hot day, with
OL,8,Fplenty of sunshine. Staying cooler
OL,9,Ftowards the coasts. Light winds
OL,10,Fthroughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHigh
OL,13,Fpressure keeping it dry and settled.
OL,14,FPlenty of sunshine and feeling hot.
OL,15,FSome overnight low cloud and fog
OL,16,Fforming each night but quickly
OL,17,Fclearing during the early mornings.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
